  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/dd88362a2494ba75a31f7c5514a70e47.avif?t=1573732648\" width=586 height=75 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/a89ab0e92206ebc28cd08a06e69189d2.apng?t=1573732648\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/a89ab0e92206ebc28cd08a06e69189d2.poster.avif?t=1573732648\" class=\"bb_img\" width=556 height=72 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>Beautiful Bricks</strong> is the ultimate 4 player brick breaker. A restoration of an arcade great with awesome improvements like physic-based ball behavior, more paddle control (including an ability to jump), 4 simultaneous players and boss battles. All presented in a consistent retro ‘8-bit’ aesthetic.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beautiful Bricks Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\t1 - 4 simultaneous players<br></li><li>\t230 levels and 15 challenging boss battles<br></li><li>\tOver 40 innovative power ups including Jet Pad (giving the paddle flight) and Wreck’n Ball (a giant ball that destroys anything in its path)<br></li><li>\tUnique physic-based ball movement and ability to have the paddle jump<br></li><li>\tPlay with keyboard, mouse or gamepad<br></li><li>\tCo-operative and competitive multiplayer modes<br></li><li>\tSpecial game modes: Endless, Boss Rush, Invader and Marathon<br></li><li>\t8-bit style graphics and sound<br></li><li>\tTracker .MOD “chiptune” style music<br></li><li>\tLocally savable high scores and achievements<br></li><li>\tUnlockable secrets and hidden content</li></ul><br><br>...and just look at that box art!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/930c7e998c88914c921dcfd9b437c155.avif?t=1573732648\" width=500 height=706 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/a65aa9b73ce39f9e95d9b6f580bc7d56.avif?t=1573732648\" width=586 height=75 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/dd88362a2494ba75a31f7c5514a70e47.avif?t=1573732648\" width=586 height=75 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/a89ab0e92206ebc28cd08a06e69189d2.apng?t=1573732648\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/a89ab0e92206ebc28cd08a06e69189d2.poster.avif?t=1573732648\" class=\"bb_img\" width=556 height=72 /></picture></span><br><br><strong>Beautiful Bricks</strong> is the ultimate 4 player brick breaker. A restoration of an arcade great with awesome improvements like physic-based ball behavior, more paddle control (including an ability to jump), 4 simultaneous players and boss battles. All presented in a consistent retro ‘8-bit’ aesthetic.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Beautiful Bricks Features</h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\t1 - 4 simultaneous players<br></li><li>\t230 levels and 15 challenging boss battles<br></li><li>\tOver 40 innovative power ups including Jet Pad (giving the paddle flight) and Wreck’n Ball (a giant ball that destroys anything in its path)<br></li><li>\tUnique physic-based ball movement and ability to have the paddle jump<br></li><li>\tPlay with keyboard, mouse or gamepad<br></li><li>\tCo-operative and competitive multiplayer modes<br></li><li>\tSpecial game modes: Endless, Boss Rush, Invader and Marathon<br></li><li>\t8-bit style graphics and sound<br></li><li>\tTracker .MOD “chiptune” style music<br></li><li>\tLocally savable high scores and achievements<br></li><li>\tUnlockable secrets and hidden content</li></ul><br><br>...and just look at that box art!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/930c7e998c88914c921dcfd9b437c155.avif?t=1573732648\" width=500 height=706 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/810060/extras/a65aa9b73ce39f9e95d9b6f580bc7d56.avif?t=1573732648\" width=586 height=75 /></span>",
